Career counselors remind attendees to maintain eye contact during their interactions. As the event progresses, students exit the gym with tote bags and a stack of business cards, while friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly. Alumni volunteers share quick pep talks near the coffee station, and the engineering society sponsors a resume review table near the stage. Workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom.
